{"tid":1077262,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"師兄指點指點，有咩要改善","createTime":"2019-03-25T12:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T03:08:14.000Z","uid":243033,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"785ff3d32cd2b6807b3416899b9eb59d54aacba8","tid":1077262,"uid":243033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:51:17.000Z","msg":"167cm 71.5kg 康文署操,冇搵教練，睇YouTube.<br />\n一星期 4-5日gym ，起身飲水熱身後空肚操，每次平均需時55min - 1hr<br />\n冇帶飯，飲食冇特別節制，凍飲走甜，唔食雞皮，一手3-4餐，有飲粉<br />\n次序如圖 A -&gt; C -&gt; B -&gt; C -&gt;之後重複<br />\n一星期打一日拳，當日同第二朝都唔操<br />\n最近好小跑，可能兩星期先跑一晚6km 30min<br />\n每次操嘅強度提升<br />\neg. 卧推 各45lb 8rep,下次就45lb9rep<br />\n-&gt; 45lb 10rep -&gt; 50lb 8 rep<br />\n如此類推，8加到10rep先轉重量要加rep<br />\n<br />\n求指教，需要多啲資料可以留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDzQ8fv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDzQ8fv.jpg&h=39b0fe8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4s8 = 4set 8rep (再額外一半嘅重量先熱身）<br />\n重量基本以lb計，除非特別注明<br />\n有時重量再+數字，數字=（我都唔知係lb定kg,部機有得紐個個位） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQ5tas4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQ5tas4.jpg&h=c23fa5a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99c3ade13406bd7ec06431d3a880702195b37812","tid":1077262,"uid":186628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"一星期 4-5日gym ，起身飲水熱身後空肚操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35759bb0f065c5e3c9a0f3541c3be4e1a3b87d8a","tid":1077262,"uid":243033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99c3ade13406bd7ec06431d3a880702195b37812","tid":1077262,"uid":186628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"一星期 4-5日gym ，起身飲水熱身後空肚操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T20:29:43.000Z","msg":"？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=